Discovered a whole new side of Ibiza from our stay at @7PinesIbiza. From the magic of Es Vedrà & unimaginable sunsets in the west, to the iconic old town in the south & the awe-striking and serene coast in the north, the destination has something for everyone.

📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels

Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico

Fall in love with this perfect getaway with @moroccanmusthaves! 😍 Located in Essaouira, Villa Anouk is built in the ancient Moroccan Beldi tradition, made entirely of stone and wood with thatched ceilings by local artisans and master craftsmen. The result is a stunning retreat that serves as a perfect base to explore the town, but also to relax and bliss out in the beautiful setting. 🇲🇦

💡 BH Tip: Villa Anouk is a prime spot for authentic Berber cooking and shouldn't be missed! If ever you're going out to explore the town and find yourself in Moulay Bouzerktoun, Villa Anouk recommends Lamawa Restaurant!

When was the last time you visited Morocco? What was your best experience here? 

📸 @moroccanmusthaves
📍 @villaanouk, Essaouira, Morocco

Be among the first to experience timeless glamour and modern sophistication as The Langham Jakarta finally opens its doors to welcome you with its legendary Langham service and hospitality that has won loyal patrons worldwide for 150 years. ✨

1. Marvel at their ten-meter lobby with bespoke lighting and stunning interiors.
2. Indulge in culinary masterpieces at their Michelin Starred restaurants: Tom’s by Tom Aikens and T’ang Court. 😋 
3. Work remotely at The Langham Club Lounge and fuel your productivity with its amenities.
4. Have afternoon tea at Alice. 🍵 
5. Drink cocktails at Artisan, located on their rooftop, where the best views of the city and sunsets can be enjoyed.
6. End your day with a rubdown at Chuan Spa. 💆🏼‍♀️ 
7. Retire for the night in one of the 223 guest rooms all lavishly furnished and spacious to suit your taste.

Celebrate The Everday at The Langham, Jakarta. ❤️

📍 @delimakmur @langham_jakarta and @langhamhotels

Be inspired like @traveljeanieous with this gorgeous view of Gaudi's La Sagrada Familia. ⛪ The Ayre Hotel Rosellón in Barcelona has surreal panoramic rooftop views of the city and is barely 200 meters away from the most iconic basilica in Spain. 🇪🇸

💡BH Trivia: Did you know that La Sagrada Familia has been under construction for over a century? This year it has been believed to have entered its final stage of construction and is estimated to be completed by 2026. 

When was the last time you visited Barcelona? What was your first reaction upon seeing this treasure? ❤

📽️ @traveljeanieous
📍 @ayrehoteles, Barcelona, Spain
🎶 Andrea Bocelli - Bésame Mucho

Come home to Puri Santrian Resort Bali where you'll be treated like family and not just as a guest! 🇮🇩 Enveloped in lush gardens and located on a tranquil beach in Sanur, immerse in strong cultural roots and true Balinese hospitality. 🙏 

Every corner of Puri Santrian is designed to make you feel at home. With lavish suites furnished with state-of-the-art amenities, it lets you unwind with the wonders of nature all around you. 😌 

Have you visited Puri Santrian? When was the last time you visited Bali? 

📍 @purisantrian, Bali, Indonesia
🎶 Joel Adams - Please Don't Go
